{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"15198-what-shall-i-wear-today","title":"Nzambara Ichi Uyumunsi?","description":"Iminsi imwe , kirakomeye kubona ikyokwambara . Umukobwa muto yagyeragyeje mu kanzu nyinsi ataraboona ikyokwambara.","language":"Kinyarwanda","langCode":"rw","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Noel Abaho"],"illustrators":["Tanvi Bhat"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Uganda Christian University","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/15198-what-shall-i-wear-today"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2289/size3/466aacc8ac4a2d255bdf88b7bf413bee.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2289/size6/466aacc8ac4a2d255bdf88b7bf413bee.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2290/size6/7980184b28e7f6bcb2d90fda93d0cad7.jpg","text":"Uja ugira ibitekyerezo ngo myenda yawe ikwireye? ego!","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2291/size6/ecdb516cd2660b5019f4ebf2e93833ee.jpg","text":"Amapesa yishati aranteganya.\nIpandalo irafata chane nigatoya.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2292/size6/96826cf309e5e88cd4a9a7733c4b3d14.jpg","text":"Igiteteya nakyo sikyankwira .","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2293/size6/9d56ce4fc2a8ea5d3ef4e1898e9e6738.jpg","text":"Ubunyonyozi ku gapandalo kangye nabwo buraryana.\nKandi ndunva ni pandalo nayo ni niini.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2294/size6/06875940a4db78a5ca65a92f15875433.jpg","text":"Natwa tupandalo twangye twiza tunfatira kumubiri noneho sinatukwiramo turanfata chaane.\nNachinu kiiza nkwiramo neeza mbona.","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2295/size6/7f93acd3e14d3d2db92f64b67eb6f494.jpg","text":"Kandi iki giteteyi kiraka chaane irangi ryakyo.\n Amashati yamurumuna wangye see? Birasesa mumaaso!","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2296/size6/326ebf0bfda0e23a0dc9ab637d84fa57.jpg","text":"Ikanzu ya papa nayo ni ndeende.\n Aga sari ka mama nako kalifashe naabi.\nIbinu ibimwe nibyiza simbibona. Ndunva nshaka","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2297/size6/667d394f746df6af60208c8d959a6994.jpg","text":"Iyi imyenda ndunva ,' iza neganya umunsi wose.'\nAriko noneho mbonye igitekyerezo...","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2298/size6/4706454e7a668323f67654ad8af60b11.jpg","text":"Nza fatanya iyimyenda namaragi yazo neeza nangye mbone ikyonambara uyumunsi!","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":9,"words":101}}